des: Fireside Aces radio is produced by Student Media, student media is a student organization at the University of Evansville. Student media produces the crescent magazine published online and in print three times a semester. Student media produces several podcasts and utilizes design, photography, video, and sound towards experiential and academic learning in journalistic endeavors and engaging storytelling. Student media elevates the voice of the student body and connects the campus and community to important information and points of view.
